              <div class="gov-c-card"><h4>Disclosed RPTs</h4><p style="font-size:0.83rem; color:var(--ink-2); line-height:1.65;">All related party transactions above LKR 50Mn are disclosed in the Annual Report and announced to the CSE. There are no undisclosed material transactions with HNB Group entities — including the parent bank.</p></div>
